== Important: Before you get started you might want to ...

  * Install the active_form plugin
    script/plugin install git://github.com/cs/active_form.git

  * Configure the mail recipient settings in app/models/contact_mailer.rb

  * Notice that the plugin generated specs if Rspec is installed

